  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >72 Total HO scenes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 chapters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Butterfly Album</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 extra locations</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 minigames</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A music player</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to embark on a new adventure with \"I Love Finding Furbabies,\" the 7th installment in the popular hidden object game franchise! In this game, you'll explore stunning environments and search for adorable furry creatures to add to your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.poster.avif?t=1729641876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.webm?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.mp4?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the piglets, kittens, ducklings, puppies, and many other furbabies as you visit many different locations! Solve relaxing puzzles and play an assortment of fun minigames while collecting all the adorable furbabies hidden in beautiful sceneries!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.poster.avif?t=1729641876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.webm?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.mp4?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the furbabies you can find in this classic hidden object game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to embark on a new adventure with \"I Love Finding Furbabies,\" the 7th installment in the popular hidden object game franchise! In this game, you'll explore stunning environments and search for adorable furry creatures to add to your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.poster.avif?t=1729641876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.webm?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/286c42a75347c0508285fd8d55d7ee2a.mp4?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the piglets, kittens, ducklings, puppies, and many other furbabies as you visit many different locations! Solve relaxing puzzles and play an assortment of fun minigames while collecting all the adorable furbabies hidden in beautiful sceneries!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.poster.avif?t=1729641876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.webm?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341780/extras/3bf04130a6722aed3784a3c0d026dd26.mp4?t=1729641876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the furbabies you can find in this classic hidden object game!</p>",
